properties.areaDesc: Melville Foothills; Southern Wheatland; Northern Sweet Grass
properties.headline: High Wind Watch issued January 5 at 3:19AM MST until January 6 at 8:00PM MST by NWS Billings MT
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 30 to 40 mph with gusts up to 60 mph
possible.

* WHERE...Northern Sweet Grass, Melville Foothills and Southern
Wheatland.

* WHEN...From this evening through Monday evening.

* IMPACTS...Travel could be difficult, especially for high profile
vehicles.
properties.instruction:
Monitor the latest forecasts and warnings for updates on this
situation. Fasten loose objects or shelter objects in a safe
location prior to the onset of winds.

Additional graphics for this hazard can be found at
http://www.weather.gov/billings

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WATCH IN EFFECT FROM THIS EVENING THROUGH MONDAY EVENING
